# Sava — environment variable reference.
#
# Secrets NEVER live in the client or the repo. Backend secrets are set via
# `wrangler secret put` (and apps/backend/.dev.vars for local dev). Client-side
# public config uses EXPO_PUBLIC_* and is inlined into the app bundle.
#
# Per-app templates:
#   apps/mobile/.env.example      (EXPO_PUBLIC_* — safe to ship)
#   apps/backend/.dev.vars.example (server secrets — never shipped)
#
# Nothing is required to run the YK-486 scaffold.
